# Intuition
Since a fixed size stack is to be implemented, we will use an Array.
# Approach
Create an array of size maxSize in the constructor function and store the top and maxSize of the stack in a variable.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
push: $$O(1)$$
pop: $$O(1)$$
increment: $$O(k)$$

- Space complexity: $$O(k)$$

