**Brute Force:**
```
public String longestNiceSubstring(String s) {
	int len = s.length();
	int[] res = {0, 0};
	for (int i = 0; i < len; i++) {
		int upper = 0;
		int lower = 0;
		for (int j = i; j < len; j++) {
			char c = s.charAt(j);
			if (c > 'Z') {
				lower |= 1 << (c-'a');
			} else {
				upper |= 1 << (c-'A');
			}
			if ((lower ^ upper) == 0 &&
				j - i + 1 > res[1] - res[0]) {
				res[0] = i;
				res[1] = j + 1;
			}
		}
	}
	return s.substring(res[0], res[1]);
}
```

**Divide and Conquer:**
```
public String longestNiceSubstring(String s) {
	return helper(s, 0, s.length());
}

String helper(String s, int left, int right) {
	int lower = 0;
	int upper = 0;
	for (int i = left; i < right; i++) {
		char c = s.charAt(i);
		if (c > 'Z') {
			lower |= 1 << (c-'a');
		} else {
			upper |= 1 << (c-'A');
		}
	}
	for (int i = left; i < right; i++) {
		char c = s.charAt(i);
		int shift = c - (c > 'Z' ? 'a' : 'A');
		if ((lower & 1 << shift) == (upper & 1 << shift)) {
			continue;
		}
		String leftStr = helper(s, left, i);
		String rightStr = helper(s, i+1, right);
		if (leftStr.length() >= rightStr.length()) {
			return leftStr;
		} else {
			return rightStr;
		}

	}
	return s.substring(left, right);
